name: Fancy Dressup
description:
Shining stars in the new issue of Hollywood Magazine. Choose the best outfit for this cute cover girl: from a basic day-to-day coloured t-shirt combined with a fancy skirt to a glamorous evening dress, you can dress her up with the ones you like best of all. Complete her look with the matching shoes and a wonderful hairstyle..
Enjoy the Dressup of this shining star !
